data.description: This charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is on a nice corner lot.  It has 2423 sq. ft. above grade, full basement and 1 1/2 stories.  There is a good sized eat-in kitchen with plenty of sunlight during the day.  The dining room has a chandelier for over the table to enlighten your family meals.  There is a spacious living room with a wood burning fireplace.  There is enough room for socializing and family gatherings.  The  main floor has 2 good sized bedrooms.  The master has a large closet with twin doors and the other bedroom has a closet that is lined with cedar.  The main floor hosts a full bathroom with a new tub/shower.  The upstairs has a large open area for additional living space or a play room.  The upstairs has a has two bedrooms with plenty of storage, as well as a half bathroom.  The full basement is partially finished consisting of three rooms.  One is perfect for an additional work out area.  The laundry/utility room has a washer and dryer, more storage and a three quarter bathroom.  The last basement room is set up as a workshop on one side and garden center and storage on the other.  The metal roof is newer and the vinyl siding is in great shape.  This house has a prolific backyard with fruits and vegetables growing.  There is a single car detached garage.  There is also a outdoor storage shed which is great for out of season items.  This home is located in a great neighborhood with friendly neighbors.
